title: Bikerumor Pic Of The Day: Marin County, California
content:
Photo submitted by Daniel Nacamuli, “Caught these two strangers at the top of a pretty tough climb from Tennessee Valley to Coastal Fire Road in Marin, California.” We always love seeing photos from where you are riding and are happy to share them with our readers around the world here on the Pic Of The Day.
